Compendium of Scales for Use

00:45:14.707 --> 00:45:16.540
in the Scholarship of
Teaching and Learning"

00:45:16.540 --> 00:45:18.820
that has lots and lots of
examples and references

00:45:18.820 --> 00:45:20.290
for scales that might be useful.

